# CODEOWNERS - Enterprise Configuration
# This file defines code owners for automated review assignment
# Format: https://help.github.com/en/articles/about-code-owners

# =============================================================================
# GLOBAL OWNERSHIP
# =============================================================================
# Default owner for all files not explicitly matched below
*    @engineering-leads

# =============================================================================
# EXECUTIVE LEADERSHIP
# =============================================================================
# C-level and VP-level oversight for critical business logic
/executive/                    @ceo @cto @vp-engineering

# =============================================================================
# ENGINEERING TEAMS
# =============================================================================
# Platform Engineering Team - Core infrastructure and shared services
/platform/                     @platform-team
/platform/infrastructure/      @platform-team @sre-team
/platform/api-gateway/         @platform-team @backend-leads

# Backend Services
/src/backend/                  @backend-team
/src/backend/api/              @backend-team @api-leads
/src/backend/services/         @backend-team
/src/backend/workers/          @backend-team @platform-team

# Frontend Applications
/src/frontend/                 @frontend-team
/src/frontend/components/      @frontend-team @design-system-team
/src/frontend/pages/           @frontend-team
/src/frontend/hooks/           @frontend-team

# Mobile Applications
/src/mobile/                   @mobile-team
/src/mobile/ios/               @ios-team
/src/mobile/android/           @android-team

# Data Engineering
/src/data/                     @data-team
/src/data/pipelines/           @data-team @platform-team
/src/data/analytics/           @data-team @analytics-team

# =============================================================================
# SECURITY & COMPLIANCE
# =============================================================================
# Security-critical code requires security team review
**/security/                   @security-team
**/auth/                       @security-team @backend-leads
**/encryption/                 @security-team
**/compliance/                 @security-team @compliance-officer
.github/workflows/security*    @security-team
.github/workflows/compliance*  @security-team @compliance-officer

# Dependency management
